{"tid":966402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【-28℃棄B】初生男嬰被丟雪地 狠母：就係想生個女","createTime":"2019-01-02T18:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T15:21:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ed9ff3df7af6754c96402c43e82e0a5300ed5c83","tid":966402,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T18:42:21.000Z","msg":"天寒地凍，最好是躲在暖暖的被窩裏，可是黑龍江省大興安嶺一名母親，卻在只有零下28℃嚴寒天氣下，將剛剛滿月的親生兒子抱到一個公園遺棄。這名男嬰在公園半日後才被人發現，凍得臉色發白，馬上被送到醫院。警方調查後找到這名棄子狠母，原來她家裏已有兩名兒子，因一心想要女兒，於是將兒子遺棄。<br />\n這名剛滿月的男嬰在上月24日，被遺棄在黑龍江省大興安嶺塔河鎮的一個公園的雪地上，被發現時只包着毛毯、棉被，身旁有兩袋嬰兒用品。男嬰除了冷得臉色發白，同時全身都有污迹，發現男嬰的民眾馬上將他送到醫院，醫護人員馬上給他檢查，同時給他熱食，當地民眾聞訊後，紛紛捐款，醫護人員指，男嬰在平安夜被發現，於是取名「平安」，希望他一生平安。<br />\n當地警方接報後開始追尋平安的身世，兩日後發現將他遺棄的張姓母親，以涉嫌遺棄罪將她拘捕，同時帶她回到公園重組案情。張女稱自己沒有固定工作，之前已生下兩名兒子，平安是意外懷孕的結果，當時以為這次懷上女兒，所以把胎兒留下，沒想到出生後還是男嬰。<br />\n張女稱平安出生後，他的丈夫已經放棄了撫養權，將平安過繼給別人，但她還是決定將他遺棄。她說家中經濟不好，要照顧兩名兒子已讓她感到吃力。雖然警方把張女拘捕，但她表示要照顧家中的兒子，警方准她回家，但不能離開居住的區域，案件已經轉交檢控機關。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pc5EuQe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPc5EuQe.png&h=7ac68044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mGc0egV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmGc0egV.png&h=38d9f8bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190103/59097717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190103%2F59097717&d=HWnlXHF9RxL95jyyV0%2FOqEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=fac9a9eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190103%2F59097717&h=420e4de7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190103/59097717</a>"},{"pid":"cda89bee5df437ab6b2cb822baeceb50e927aa84","tid":966402,"uid":90820,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T18:55:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當時<span style=\"color: red;\">以為</span>這次懷上女兒</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d0680013f1e133a52846ee0ff5606f5ab9c966","tid":966402,"uid":96704,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T19:02:01.000Z","msg":"個B: <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40ced68455377a138a1c688a4f8208f63a41282","tid":966402,"uid":161144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T19:06:19.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"19de76329632abb7f6c32ebd26cf8fa3ecf35120","tid":966402,"uid":6192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T19:07:46.000Z","msg":"Cls"},{"pid":"e99acec966547e9065a4a3c3db55578fe18256d8","tid":966402,"uid":66714,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T19:10:41.000Z","msg":"好似第一次聽要女唔要仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0a8f464849193c8de505e6c1d3c5516987ecd3","tid":966402,"uid":43173,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T19:17:22.000Z","msg":"完全唔洗估都中"},{"pid":"9c1094d87942eac8ed3f8647f82e90af96c01661","tid":966402,"uid":32114,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"quote":{"pid":"e99acec966547e9065a4a3c3db55578fe18256d8","tid":966402,"uid":66714,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T19:10:41.000Z","msg":"好似第一次聽要女唔要仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T19:19:21.000Z","msg":"想生個女做雞養家<br />\n地獄鬼國不意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d5b58601c2d6d56437dc7cb398dc699cd7f0e1","tid":966402,"uid":11148,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"e99acec966547e9065a4a3c3db55578fe18256d8","tid":966402,"uid":66714,"like":60,"dislike":0,"scor